00:42:43,950 --> 00:42:46,070
He's kind when he's kind.

568
00:42:46,070 --> 00:42:50,670
When he's angry, you can guess...

569
00:42:51,830 --> 00:42:54,590
Tien's just like that.

570
00:42:54,590 --> 00:42:55,870
He's always crazy.

571
00:42:58,030 --> 00:42:59,670
But, he is the closest to me.

572
00:43:00,230 --> 00:43:02,310
Maybe because we always hang out together.

573
00:43:02,310 --> 00:43:04,390
And Chan is my little brother.

574
00:43:04,390 --> 00:43:06,630
He lives with mom, so I don't see him a lot.

575
00:43:10,350 --> 00:43:14,830
After my parents separated, Nuea and Tien lived with dad.

576
00:43:14,830 --> 00:43:16,670
Chan and I lived with mom.

577
00:43:16,670 --> 00:43:21,510
But, we're still in contact with each other.

578
00:43:31,230 --> 00:43:32,270
Tai.

579
00:43:40,230 --> 00:43:41,950
Let me ask you this question.

580
00:43:44,390 --> 00:43:48,230
Does the relationship between your mom and dad...

581
00:43:48,230 --> 00:43:50,950
still affect your thought of the soul mates?

582
00:43:55,590 --> 00:43:57,070
-Dad!
 -Well...

583
00:43:57,070 --> 00:43:58,550
Dad! Wait!

584
00:43:58,550 --> 00:44:03,590
What happened between mom and dad still lingers around.

585
00:44:04,790 --> 00:44:05,990
It never goes away.

586
00:44:10,430 --> 00:44:11,350
Dad!

587
00:44:17,110 --> 00:44:20,110
I tried to cure my hearing loss.

588
00:44:21,350 --> 00:44:23,230
I wanted to be a normal man.

589
00:44:25,510 --> 00:44:31,230
But, I don't want to be that normal anymore.

590
00:45:05,310 --> 00:45:06,910
Thank you, Patts.

591
00:45:09,070 --> 00:45:10,510
Thank you, too.

592
00:45:32,390 --> 00:45:34,150
Let's get in the car?

593
00:45:35,790 --> 00:45:39,150
Maybe my place? We are almost there.

594
00:45:39,550 --> 00:45:41,430
Your car is quite far from us.

595
00:45:41,580 --> 00:45:44,590
So I can get into your place?

596
00:45:44,750 --> 00:45:47,750
Um, yeah.

597
00:45:50,030 --> 00:45:50,670
Let's go.

598
00:45:50,670 --> 00:45:56,030
Tai, here. We won't get wet then.

599
00:46:37,910 --> 00:46:39,780
You change your shoes first.

600
00:46:39,780 --> 00:46:40,910
Okay.

601
00:46:50,950 --> 00:46:53,070
My room is a bit messy. I'm sorry.

602
00:46:57,510 --> 00:46:59,150
No, it doesn't.

603
00:46:59,150 --> 00:47:02,750
Not as neat as your place.

604
00:47:07,590 --> 00:47:09,150
(Meow)

605
00:47:12,630 --> 00:47:13,950
Duer...

606
00:47:25,350 --> 00:47:27,710
I've been a vet for so long,

607
00:47:27,710 --> 00:47:30,030
but I have never envied a cat as much as I do now.

608
00:47:42,790 --> 00:47:44,550
You want to get changed?

609
00:47:44,550 --> 00:47:46,180
I'll go get you the dry clothes.

610
00:47:46,350 --> 00:47:47,270
Okay.

611
00:48:07,230 --> 00:48:12,390
These are my biggest clothes.

612
00:48:21,950 --> 00:48:23,190
Thank you.

613
00:48:26,590 --> 00:48:28,790
Where's the bathroom?

614
00:48:31,510 --> 00:48:32,550
The left side.

615
00:48:49,070 --> 00:48:51,710
Tai, do you have a bath towel...

616
00:48:55,470 --> 00:48:56,870
I'm sorry!

617
00:49:07,670 --> 00:49:10,670
Tai, do you have a bath towel?

618
00:49:25,750 --> 00:49:27,230
Here you are.

619
00:49:29,550 --> 00:49:30,990
Thank you.

620
00:49:51,350 --> 00:49:53,830
I wanted you to go to Doi Mae Pliang.

621
00:49:54,830 --> 00:49:56,630
A Veterinary Volunteering Camp.

622
00:49:56,630 --> 00:49:58,190
Are you thinking what I'm thinking now?

623
00:49:59,750 --> 00:50:01,630
Your shoulders are so soft.

624
00:50:03,350 --> 00:50:04,670
Patts, stop!
